🚀 Final Takeaways

✔ Catch errors at the DB client initialization level.
✔ Throw DatabaseInitializationException instead of letting the app crash.
✔ Use GlobalExceptionHandler to return clean API responses (500 Internal Server Error).
✔ Log all failures (CosmosException, IllegalArgumentException, unexpected exceptions).

